---
import heroVideo from '../assets/video.mp4'
---

<section
	class='w-full max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 py-16 md:py-32 flex flex-col md:flex-row items-center justify-between gap-10 md:gap-12'
>
	<div
		class='w-full md:w-1/2 flex flex-col items-center md:items-start text-center md:text-left z-10'
	>
		<h1
			class='text-4xl sm:text-5xl md:text-6xl font-bold leading-tight mb-4 md:mb-6 text-balance'
		>
			Porque una voz que se <span class='text-terracotta italic font-serif'>guarda</span>
			es una <span class='italic font-serif'>historia</span> que no muere.
		</h1>
		<p
			class='text-base sm:text-lg text-charcoal/80 mb-8 max-w-lg font-sans px-2 md:px-0'
		>
			Somos un equipo dedicado a preservar el legado familiar a través de
			historias y recuerdos inolvidables plasmados en algo <span
				class='italic font-serif'>atemporal</span
			>.
		</p>
		<a href="#como-funciona"
			class='inline-block text-center w-full sm:w-auto bg-terracotta text-offwhite px-8 py-4 rounded-full font-medium tracking-wide hover:bg-terracotta/90 transition-colors shadow-lg shadow-terracotta/20 text-lg'
		>
			Comienza tu historia
		</a>
	</div>
	<div
		class='w-full md:w-1/2 relative flex justify-center md:justify-end mt-4 md:mt-0'
	>
		<!-- Soft mask trick using gradient and CSS mask -->
		<div
			class='relative w-full max-w-sm md:max-w-md aspect-square md:aspect-[3/4] rounded-2xl overflow-hidden shadow-inner'
			style='mask-image: radial-gradient(circle at center, black 65%, transparent 100%); -webkit-mask-image: radial-gradient(circle at center, black 65%, transparent 100%);'
		>
			<video
				src={heroVideo}
				autoplay
				loop
				muted
				playsinline
				class='w-full h-full object-cover grayscale opacity-90 hover:scale-105 transition-transform duration-1000 origin-center'
			></video>
		</div>
	</div>
</section>
